    "288 Cusumano [307] 2023 Technology \"AI hallucination\" occurs when LLMs, in the absence of an answer to a query, use predictive analytics to make up reasonable but sometimes incorrect responses.",
    "Continued on next pageTABLE V -continued from previous page Num.",
    "Author(s) Year Application Definition Citation 289 Nashid et al. [308] 2023 Large Language Model \"AI hallucination\" refers to ChatGPT's outputs that are incorrect or nonsensical.",
    "290 Pataranutaporn et al. [309] 2023 Technology \"AI hallucination\" refers to the phenomenon where ChatGPT generates content that is nonsensical or unfaithful to the provided source content.",
    "291 Faggioli et al. [310] 2023 Large Language Model \"AI hallucination\" occurs when LLMs generate text that contains inaccurate or false information, often in an affirmative manner that makes it difficult for humans to even suspect errors."
